<th>direction</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>the snake is swimming <b>inside</b> the dog</td>
<td><span class="gloss">long-animal</span> <span class="gloss">do</span> <span class="gloss">water-move</span> <span class="gloss-emph">inside</span> <span class="gloss">dog</span></td>
<td>static</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>the snake is swimming <b>into</b> the dog</td>
